flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> GatherReq[Gather frontend requirements]
    GatherReq --> IdentifyEntities[Identify entities and attributes]
    IdentifyEntities --> DefineRelations[Define relationships]
    DefineRelations --> DecideNorm{Normalization required?}
    DecideNorm -->|Yes| Normalize[Normalize schema]
    DecideNorm -->|No| SkipNorm[Keep as is]
    Normalize --> DefineConstraints[Define constraints and keys]
    SkipNorm --> DefineConstraints
    DefineConstraints --> DesignERD[Create ER diagram]
    DesignERD --> ReviewSchema[Review with stakeholders]
    ReviewSchema --> Approved{Approved?}
    Approved -->|Yes| Finalize[Finalize database design]
    Approved -->|No| Revise[Revise design]
    Revise --> IdentifyEntities
    Finalize --> End([End])